/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"Subaru 有東洋Benz 之稱係因為維修貴零件貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係因為好車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"其實掃把佬好襟揸，外國大把十幾廿年嘅掃把仲係行得走得冇小問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bdab4d95b82bd6d31e0eaf8a85a1763e0d4e36","tid":521674,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過XC60/ 嚟緊既XC40<br />\nVolvo 岩雪地渣，內籠又靚，馬力又夠"},{"pid":"0fcb9bc2b7e6c099f8a73d5736aa68a7a64a5314","tid":521674,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T21:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁老老實實wo<br />\n買X1不如買CX5<br />\n一係上X3</blockquote>外國落雪一定唔會買Mazda 同 BMW依啲假四驅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識揸識上鏈兩驅都冇問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Acoi3SF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAcoi3SF.jpg&h=a33e9bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n揸返半山屋如履平地指住兩邊落晒坑既四驅SUV/Pickup嚟笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係揸過雪地既人都知雪呔雪鏈重要過有AWD。</blockquote>係雪地AWD 安全過2WD 係冇得拗<br />\n係外國做過戶外活動教練，年年冬天都上十次雪山，見過大把前驅車因為大雪就算有雪胎雪鏈都冇用</blockquote><br />\n加速上AWD喺雪地係有優勢過2wd。<br />\n但剎車時AWD冇持別優勢。</blockquote>唔係話加速優勢，而係路面不平同多雪嘅位冇咁易會困住走唔到，特別係朝早有積雪嘅時候</blockquote><br />\n我似我咁有鏈既話除非突然前面有大舊雪高到上bumber位，否則都係冇野困得住。<br />\n<br />\n可惜當年未有車cam, show唔到俾你睇我揸返屋企段路有幾斜同幾多雪。<br />\n唔係話AWD冇用或唔夠2WD好。<br />\n不過以我十幾年雪地經驗，有雪呔/鏈遠遠重要過有冇AWD。美國caranddriver做過個test之後都係有同樣結論。"},{"pid":"624ffb49b5e346434838db9f0c2ea9049637be32","tid":521674,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T21:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><bloc